---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | EB-1A Green Card Coach" description="Read the Privacy Policy for EB-1A Green Card Coach website.">

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container legal-inner">
      <h1 class="heading-1 legal-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <hr class="divider" />

      <div class="legal-content">

        <p class="text-body">At Eb1agreencardcoach (<a href="https://www.eb1agreencardcoach.com" class="legal-link">www.eb1agreencardcoach.com</a>), safeguarding the privacy of our visitors is one of our top priorities. This policy covers online activities and information shared through the website only, not offline collection methods. By using the website, visitors agree to the terms outlined in this privacy document.</p>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-body">The organization specifies what personal data it requests and why. When visitors contact the company directly, they may share names, email addresses, phone numbers, addresses, message contents, and attachments. Account registration may request contact information including names, company names, addresses, emails, and telephone numbers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Collected data serves multiple purposes:</p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li>Operating and maintaining the website</li>
            <li>Enhancing and personalizing user experience</li>
            <li>Analyzing website usage</li>
            <li>Developing new products, services, features, and functionality</li>
            <li>Direct and partner communications for customer service, updates, marketing, and promotional purposes</li>
            <li>Sending emails</li>
            <li>Identifying and preventing fraud</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Log Files</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Standard log files track visitor information including IP addresses, browser types, ISP details, timestamps, referring/exit pages, and click counts. This data analyzes trends and gathers demographics but remains unlinked to personally identifiable information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Cookies and Web Beacons</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Cookies store visitor preferences and browsing history to customize web page content based on browser type and other factors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Third-Party Advertising Policies</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Third-party ad servers or ad networks may use technologies like cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons in advertisements. The company disclaims control over these third-party technologies and recommends reviewing external privacy policies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">CCPA Privacy Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Florida consumers may request disclosure of collected personal data categories, request deletion of personal information, and request that the business avoid selling their data. Responses must occur within one month.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">GDPR Data Protection Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Individuals have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> Requesting copies of personal data (possible small fee)</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> Requesting corrections to inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> Requesting deletion, subject to conditions</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong> Requesting processing limitations, subject to conditions</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Object to Processing:</strong> Objecting to data processing, subject to conditions</li>
            <li><strong>Right to Data Portability:</strong> Requesting data transfer to another organization</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-body">A one-month response timeframe applies to all requests.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Children's Information</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Protecting children's privacy online is important to us. The organization doesn't knowingly collect personally identifiable information from those under 13. Parents should contact us immediately if children provide such information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Policy Changes</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Updates may occur periodically. Changes take effect immediately upon posting to the website.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">Contact Information</h2>
          <ul class="contact-list">
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@eb1agreencardcoach.com" class="legal-link">contact@eb1agreencardcoach.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+13054899346" class="legal-link">(305) 489-9346</a></li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> 1580 Sawgrass Corporate Pkwy, Suite 130 Sunrise, FL 33323</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-inner { max-width: 860px; }
  .legal-title { margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); }

  .legal-content {
    margin-top: var(--sp-10);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
  }

  .legal-section { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-4); }
  .legal-heading { color: var(--color-navy); }

  .legal-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: var(--sp-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .legal-list li,
  .contact-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
  }

  .legal-link {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .legal-link:hover { color: var(--color-primary-dark); }
</style>
